Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:24:34.12,WM,,0,0,0,,masssterchief
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:01.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.88,0:00:03.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Family day?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.20,0:00:05.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're also going to participate, so I leave that to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.07,0:00:06.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.32,0:00:09.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to invite the families of our colleagues and show them around the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.26,0:00:10.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So it's like a class visit then?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.07,0:00:13.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If anything, it's a cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forget how much fun the preparation on the day before the event,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:18.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that is the reason that I'm in this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:19.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.71,0:00:21.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-kun from Department 1 is heading up the whole project.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:23.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:23.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:26.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Should we make a Manten-kun t-shirts for Deparment 3?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:28.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get hyped more than Department 1 and 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.64,0:00:29.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.45,0:00:30.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Komukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.92,0:00:31.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:34.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get started then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 1 is in charge of the main event.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:38.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 2 is in charge of the food and beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.03,0:00:39.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And Department 3 is in charge of the kids' space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.04,0:00:42.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The families of our colleagues are our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.54,0:00:43.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:46.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's going to be a tough day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.05,0:00:48.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Clients?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's create something that is enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:51.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is this work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.72,0:00:55.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The main event is to conduct a tour of the company in the style of a real-life escape game.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.77,0:00:58.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This seems like something that me and my kids can enjoy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.38,0:01:03.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,After completion, they will get a newspaper with the list of internal achievements of the participating employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:06.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Every employee is the star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This matches with today's trends, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:10.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What about someone without any achievements?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.31,0:01:17.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There is no such person.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:19.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:25.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We can enjoy dishes from different countries for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.15,0:01:27.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,An around the world buffet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.04,0:01:28.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Be mindful about the amount of food and the budget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:29.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.45,0:01:30.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.80,0:01:33.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So, tell me about the Department 3's proposal for the kids' space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.32,0:01:44.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ring toss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:45.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ring toss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.23,0:01:48.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you brought a proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:50.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's only a ring toss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:57.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to think about it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:57.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:03:00.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do for family day?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:02.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I haven't decided just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:03.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What? It's this weekend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.93,0:03:06.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I couldn't come up with a project that will be green lit by Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:08.59,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,He's always working 24/7, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:10.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The power of the Ace is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let us do what we want, it's not work after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:15.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:21.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's Gunplas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:22.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Kijimura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Z'GOK!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.36,0:03:27.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that a stack of plastic models?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.44,0:03:28.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,DOM!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Jet stream attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:33.98,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you going to open a plastic model shop or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.73,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,At the shop that Riko-san introduced me to, I ended up buying it because of Chiemi-san's passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:42.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like the increasing amount of boxes is the representation of our intimacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:43.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What an easy customer, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.69,0:03:44.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:45.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:45.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:46.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Avante!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:47.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.19,0:03:49.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Avante!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:50.97,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that a Dragon Quest spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:51.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:54.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a mini 4WD!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.70,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't know that there's a RS model of Avante.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is there a Thunder Shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:01.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Fire Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:02.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shining Scorpion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:03.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mammoth Dump Truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:04.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Wildsaurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:06.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lunch Box Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in the shoes of the one being named!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:10.65,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is cool, don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.65,0:04:12.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, it's the Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:14.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The name "Emperor" is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nobody can go against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't say weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:18.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do they move?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:18.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:19.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to say it one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:20.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it's a mini 4WD!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's with the mini 4WD?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:28.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having the time of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:34.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right, we are preparing for the family day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The young ones wanted to play with mini 4WD, isn't that right Komukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:38.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is going with mini 4WD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.74,0:04:42.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.76,0:04:47.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.39,0:04:51.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You heard him, so I'm counting on you, Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:53.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD race, FUNFUN Cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're part ot the Events Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:04:59.82,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's with this proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:02.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are better options than this, like VR attractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I can lend you the gear that we used before for an event.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:06.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it okay with you, Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:10.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:13.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:15.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is something that Komukai-san came up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Asai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:21.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Department 3 is in charge of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:23.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Proceed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:28.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:32.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san gave his approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.95,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:37.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright Komukai, we're going all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:37.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,All out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.92,0:05:38.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to build a huge circuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.78,0:05:43.71,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and invite Mini 4WD Fighter to commentate on the races!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's going to be so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD Fighter? \N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is he your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.40,0:05:51.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course he's not my friend, he's a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.64,0:05:52.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You don't know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:53.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Riko, does Shinji really like plastic models?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.48,0:05:59.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course, he always bought something when he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I won't approve of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It looks like Shinji-kun likes to stack plastic model boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:06.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We don't sell plastic models for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:09.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yassan, you are wavering too much between your business and your beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.10,0:06:10.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the plastic models are sad because it's untouched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Of course I want him to build them, but he's our rare regular customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.22,0:06:15.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why are you defending him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:16.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,His goal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:18.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are you looking for today, Zakunee?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD was first released in 1982.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,With a price that was affordable to elementary school kids,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:27.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,you became an owner once you bought one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.80,0:06:29.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,you became a mechanic once you made modifications,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:31.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,and you can become a racer once you took it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:38.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's the world's first motorsport.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:48.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Children can feel the infinite possibilities of the future or the world in the palm of their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:51.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone wants to be a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This year marks the 40th anniversary of the Mini 4WD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.42,0:06:56.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There are more than 400 types of cars that went on sale,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,the total lifetime sales sits at more than 180 million units.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.01,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It created a social phenomenon in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't control it,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.39,0:07:07.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Once it's up and running, you just watch over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:09.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Just watching over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Mini 4WD takes adults back to their youth,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,kids go crazy over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:15.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In other words, adults go crazy over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:16.35,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:18.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It means that everyone can enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go to a whole new world, Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:31.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai... \N-Wait a second, Riko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Please invite me if you're going to the plastic model shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:33.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Shinji-kun, Yajima Model Shop is having second thoughts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:37.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Second thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:40.89,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems like Chiemi-chan actually wants you to build those plastic models.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.26,0:07:42.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:43.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're quick to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So please invite me next time you're going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:46.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're quick to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're just getting started?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:51.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm going to lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get this all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:56.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You just push it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:05.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.51,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm going to get you up and running in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:14.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This is nerve racking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:57.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:07.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:14.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What do you think about my youth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It was nerve racking thinking about whether it will return to me or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,This sure makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:33.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The sound is amazing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:35.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Woah, that's something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.92,0:09:37.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey, it makes you get a nosebleed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:38.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:44.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what Komukai-san has to say about the newspaper sample...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's Victory Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did you used to play with this too, Oishi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:52.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:56.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You used to play with Mini 4WD, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:09:59.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:03.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You liked it, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,When I read Komukai-san's proposal,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:10.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was so excited that I almost let out a scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You should have told us earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So, how about tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:16.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow? \N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:19.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We're going to race after we finished building our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's precisely because it's on the day before the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Rehearsal is an important part of the job, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:27.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's get hyped for the FUNFUN Cup eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.09,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's modify our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:34.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Modify?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:34.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.91,0:10:37.31,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Modification is the best part of mini 4WD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It seems like modification is an obsession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:43.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The one that is the best at cornering, wins the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.63,0:10:48.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Speed or cornering, it all depends on the course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:52.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What kind of modifications are you going to make, Komukai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:53.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:55.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You have to make modifications, or you're not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with not winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:02.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm happy if it came back to me in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:03.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So, I'm not going to do anything to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.13,0:11:05.87,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.24,0:11:18.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's make modifications after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:28.22,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:30.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You came all the way just to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:31.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.66,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Last confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you for compiling things that sounds like my achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,that is your actual achievements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:52.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Oishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.55,0:11:56.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is making modifications dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.47,0:11:58.81,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.95,0:12:00.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:02.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.72,0:12:05.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.13,0:12:08.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:13.26,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:14.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:18.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Woah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.84,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I've gathered all the necessary parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:27.45,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:28.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The cars hit this section right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:34.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're not going to start making modifications??
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:37.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We have to know the characteristics of the course before making modifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.56,0:12:49.69,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're taking that off too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:50.49,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:12:56.78,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,For super fast gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.00,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,we use Hyper-Dash Motor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:01.63,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.45,0:13:05.58,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's like soy sauce on top of rice with egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:06.83,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You can't go without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.83,0:13:08.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Next up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:18.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,We going to change the normal tires to large diameter narrow lightweight tires.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Large diameter narrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.19,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:40.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,So thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:50.33,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Make sure the rollers are straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:53.13,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:01.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:03.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:15.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Can it move?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.61,0:14:20.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.18,0:14:23.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's finally time for the meat removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.41,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Meat removal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:27.18,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,First of all, we're going to take off the stickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.18,0:14:28.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Because it's called meat removal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.48,0:14:32.57,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I have another one with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:38.92,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Gently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:09.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Meat removal, complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:10.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.29,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Have you always liked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:18.91,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Victory Magnum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:23.16,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:28.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's more like I long for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.14,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You long for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:30.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:34.27,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's because back in elementary school, this one was everyone's hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:39.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's a machine that screams protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.15,0:16:42.48,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I see that it was really popular back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I really wanted one, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.32,0:16:49.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,after I saw this at the store
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.10,0:16:53.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I began having second thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.11,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I didn't buy it in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I thought that you always have the life of a protagonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Why do you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.25,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,You're way off the mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.94,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:28.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,If we're done building it, we have to say "Give birth!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.32,0:17:28.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.06,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:34.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Victory Magnum, give birth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:36.86,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did I say it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:37.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:49.52,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Speed is everything, even light is jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Lightning Avante Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.75,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The emperor of love that rules over all corners,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:57.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Emperor Chiemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The protagonist that is late to the party,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:02.62,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Big Stone Victory Magnum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Big Stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.88,Upper,,0,0,0,,[His name literally means Big Stone]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:08.20,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.47,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:10.99,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.15,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It sure can jump high.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Inuzuka-san's Avante is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,A master at going off course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.88,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Your Emperor is too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.88,0:18:46.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I put too much emphasis on cornering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:49.02,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Magnum is running smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:54.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san, just by having it come back in one piece makes me happy after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.08,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I want to show this to you back in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:07.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I used a pomade for the first time in 2nd grade and made my pompadour debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:11.10,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I used to go to cram school 6 days a week, so I don't have any recollection of playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.10,0:19:13.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The snacks for our field trip was Apolo chocolate and Hi-Chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.36,0:19:15.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That doesn't change much between our generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:17.42,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I modified the handle of my bike to look like a Harley-Davidson handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:21.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Every week I would swap the rankings of my favorite girls and write them down in my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:23.04,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:24.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That ain't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:27.50,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm proud of this fact, I was the one who wore Levi's first on our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was aiming for all 3's for my report card, so I purposely ran slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:33.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The whole class found out that I had a crush on the teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.44,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,it was hell on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Did the teacher called you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.93,0:19:36.46,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:37.34,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.68,0:19:39.61,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you were popular back in the day, Oishi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:40.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:44.40,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I wasn't in the position to invite people to go play together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:46.17,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I was always waiting for someone to invite me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.17,0:19:47.60,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That is so surprising to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I mean, when we had to split into groups of two,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:53.05,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,my heart was beating so fast because I was so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.32,0:19:55.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,In my case, I called them out all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:57.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,How does that work actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:02.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is it like when you're out with 4 other friends, but you can't seem to join their conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:03.72,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:07.64,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Before you know it, they're talking among themselves and you're all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.64,0:20:09.93,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,It's not like you're being excluded or anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,And you can't give a good response when they actually speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:16.30,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Pretending to listen to their conversation, but in reality you space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I totally get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.35,0:20:19.07,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:22.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,The two of you sounds like two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.21,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:28.12,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I feel like the two of you are going to be best buddies if you're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I think that probably neither of us will call each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:39.24,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Even if we talk to each other, it's not going to be interesting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.92,0:20:56.43,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:11.79,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.55,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you want to play at the rooftop tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.56,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are you ready everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.36,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Ready? Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Komukai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.13,0:21:48.38,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Everyone is excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.38,0:21:49.28,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.53,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do you like that band?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.84,0:21:54.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:21:59.96,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.20,0:22:02.68,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:05.37,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.09,0:22:11.39,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:15.32,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.52,0:22:16.67,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.24,0:22:20.54,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.78,0:22:22.80,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Are the two of you a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:24.03,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.76,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Do we look like a couple?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:27.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:29.77,Default 1080p,,0,0,0,,